{"title":"[USACO Oct09] 零用钱","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"url":"http://cogs.pro:8080/cogs/problem/problem.php?pid=vmXxQkaPU","statement":[{"title":"# 题目描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h3>\n\t【题目描述】\n</h3>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t作為創造產奶紀錄的回報，Farmer John決定開始每個星期給Bessie一點零花錢。\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\tFJ有一些硬幣，一共有N (1 &lt;= N &lt;= 20)種不同的面額。每一個面額都能整除所有比它大<br/>\n的面額。\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t他想用給定的硬幣的集合，每個星期至少給Bessie某個零花錢的數目C (1 &lt;= C &lt;= <br/>\n100000000)。請幫他計算他最多能支付多少個星期的零花錢。\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;font-size:12.800000190734863px;line-height:15.199999809265137px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">題目名稱: allow</span> \n</p>\n<h3>\n\t【输入格式】\n</h3>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t輸入格式:\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t* 第一行: 兩個由空格隔開的整數: N 和 C\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t* 第2到第N+1行: 每一行有兩個整數表示一個面額的硬幣：硬幣面額V (1 &lt;= V &lt;= <br/>\n 100,000,000)和Farmer John擁有的該面額的硬幣數B (1 &lt;= B &lt;=<br/>\n        1,000,000).\n</p>\n<h3>\n\t【输出格式】\n</h3>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;font-size:12.800000190734863px;line-height:15.199999809265137px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">* 第一行: 一個單獨的整數，表示Farmer John最多能給Bessie支付多少個星期至少為C的</span><br/>\n<span style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;font-size:12.800000190734863px;line-height:15.199999809265137px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\"> 零用錢。</span> \n</p>\n<h3>\n\t【样例输入】\n</h3>\n<pre>3 6\n10 1\n1 100\n5 120</pre>\n<h3>\n\t【样例输出】\n</h3>\n<pre>111</pre>\n<h3>\n\t【提示】\n</h3>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\t輸入細節:\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:&#39;YaHei Consolas Hybrid&#39;, sans-serif;margin-left:auto;font-size:12.800000190734863px;background-color:#FEFEF2;\">\n\tFJ想要每個星期給Bessie六美分。他有100個1美分硬幣，120個5美分硬幣，和一個10美分<br/>\n硬幣。\n</p>\n<h3>\n\t【来源】\n</h3>\n<p>\n\tUSACO Contest 2009 October Gold\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/waterfalleagle/articles/1589190.html\">http://www.cnblogs.com/waterfalleagle/articles/1589190.html</a> \n</p>\n\n"}]}